casebody.data:
MILBERG LLP, et al., petitioners,
v.
Lance LABER. No. 15-734. Supreme Court of the United States June 19, 2017.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari *2263granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit for further consideration in light of Microsoft Corp. v. Baker, 582 U.S. ----, 137 S.Ct. 1702, 198 L.Ed.2d 132 (2017).
